e('id',$full_consumable->product_id)->first();\n                        $unit = InventoryUnits::where('id', $inventory_product->unit)->first();\n                        // Log::info(gettype((int) $key+1));\n                        $salesLineEndpoint =   'http://34.195.156.236:7048/BC230/api/Nexus/apollo/v1.0/companies(('.$company.'))/salesLinesBuffer';\n\n                            $patient_type = \"IP\";\n\n\n\n                        $salesLineData = [\n                            \"documentType\"=> \"Invoice\",\n                            \"documentNo\"=>$invoice['invoice_no'],\n                            \"lineNo\"=> $line_count,\n                            \"type\"=> \"Inventory\",\n                            \"no\"=>$inventory_product->item_no,\n                            \"description\"=> $inventory_product->name,\n                            \"unitPrice\" => (int) $prescription['payment']['price'],\n                            \"unitOfMeasure\" => $unit->name,\n                            \"patientTypeCode\"=> $patient_type,\n                            \"departmentCode\"=> \"\",\n                            \"quantity\" => (int) $prescription['payment']['quantity'],\n                            \"locationCode\" =>  $store->code,\n                            \"amountExclVAT\" => (int) $prescription['payment']['amount'],\n                            \"amountInclVAT\" => 0,\n                            \"vatAmount\" => 0,\n\n\n\n                        ];\n\n                        $jsonData = '{';\n                            foreach ($salesLineData as $key => $value)\n                            if (is_int($value) && $key!=\"documentNo\" && $key!=\"lineNo\") {\n                                // If value is integer, no quotes needed\n                                $jsonData .= \"\\\"$key\\\":$value,\";\n                            } else\n                            {\n                                $jsonData .= \"\\\"$key\\\":\\\"\" . (is_bool($value) ? ($value ? 'true' : 'false') : $value) . \"\\\",\";\n                            }\n                        $jsonData = rtrim($jsonData, ',') . '}';\n                        $singleQuotedData = $jsonData;\n\n                        Log::info($singleQuotedData);\n                        $curl = curl_init();\n                        curl_setopt_array($curl, array(\n                            CURLOPT_URL => $salesLineEndpoint,\n                            CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER => true,\n                            CURLOPT_ENCODING => '',\n                            CURLOPT_MAXREDIRS => 10,\n                            CURLOPT_TIMEOUT => 0,\n                            CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION => true,\n                            CURLOPT_HTTP_VERSION => CURL_HTTP_VERSION_1_1,\n                            CURLOPT_HTTPAUTH => CURLAUTH_NTLM,\n                            CURLOPT_USERPWD=> $credentials,\n                            CURLOPT_CUSTOMREQUEST => 'POST',\n                            CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS =>$singleQuotedData,\n                            CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER => array(\n                                'Content-Type: application/json'\n                            ),\n                        ));\n\n                        $response = curl_exec($curl);\n                        $status_code = curl_getinfo($curl, CURLINFO_HTTP_CODE); // Get the HTTP status code\n                        curl_close($curl);\n                        // $result = json_decode($response['invoice_id'], true);\n                        $result = $response;\n\n                        Log::info('Sales Line');\n                        Log::info($result);\n                        $line_count++;\n                    }\n\n\n              return  $singleQuotedData;\n\n            } else {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            // Handle exceptions here\n            Log::error('An error occurred: ' . $e->getMessage());\n            return false; // Or handle the error as required\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    /*\n     * update the bills\n     * */\n    public function updateIndividualBills ($data, $split_bill, $invoice)\n    {\n        $grouped_bills = collect($data['selected'])->groupBy('type');\n\n        foreach($grouped_bills as $group => $bills) {\n\n            if(!empty($bills)) {\n\n                // prescriptions\n                if($group === 'prescription') {\n                    foreach ($bills as $drug) {\n                        $p = Prescriptions::find($drug['item_id']);\n                        $p->payment()->update(['split_bill_id' => $split_bill->id]);\n                    }\n                }\n\n                // investigations\n                if($group === 'investigation') {\n                    foreach ($bills as $investigation) {\n                        $p = Investigations::find($investigation['item_id']);\n                        $p->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                        $p->save();\n                    }\n                }\n\n\n                // ward charges\n                if($group === \"Ward charge\") {\n                    foreach ($bills as $charge) {\n                        $p = InpatientVisitWard::find($charge['item_id']);\n                        $p->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                        $p->save();\n                    }\n                }\n\n                // visit charges\n                if($group === \"Admission + Daily charges\") {\n                    foreach ($bills as $visit_charge) {\n                        $p = InpatientVisitCharge::find($visit_charge['item_id']);\n                        $p->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                        $p->save();\n                    }\n                }\n\n                // consumables\n                if($group === 'consumable') {\n                    foreach ($bills as $consumable) {\n                        $p = Consumable::findOrFail($consumable['item_id']);\n                        $p->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                        $p->save();\n                    }\n                }\n\n                if($group === 'rebate') {\n                    foreach($bills as $item) {\n                        $rebate = InpatientVisitRebate::findOrFail($item['item_id']);\n\n                        $company = Insurance::where('name', 'NHIF')->first();\n\n                        $scheme = $company->schemes()->where('name', 'LIKE', '%' . 'universal' . '%')->first();\n\n                        if (!$rebate->invoice_id) {\n                            $inv = new Invoice;\n                            $inv->invoice_no = finance_generate_invoice_no();\n                            $inv->invoice_no_prefix = m_setting('finance.invoice_prefix') ? m_setting('finance.invoice_prefix') : 'INV';\n                            $inv->visit = $split_bill->visit_id;\n                            $inv->user_id = doe()->id;\n                            $inv->amount = $item['price'];\n\n                            $inv->company_id = $company->id;\n                            $inv->scheme_id = @$scheme->id;\n                            $inv->save();\n\n                            $rebate->update([\n                                'invoice_id' => $inv->id\n                            ]);\n\n                            $this->saveInvoiceItems($inv, $data);\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function createInterimBillItems($invoice, $data, $split_bill)\n    {\n        foreach($data['selected'] as $item) {\n            $type = $item['type'];\n\n            if($type == 'prescription')\n            {\n                $p = Prescriptions::find($item['item_id']);\n\n                $record = Prescriptions::setEagerLoads([])->where('id', $item['item_id'])->select(\n                    \"visit\", \"user\", \"drug\", \"take\", \"whereto\", \"method\", \"duration\", \"stop_reason\",\n                    \"stopped\", \"status\", \"allow_substitution\", \"time_measure\", \"quantity\", \"type\",\n                    \"notes\", \"canceled\", \"facility_id\", \"admission_id\", \"for_discharge\", \"for_admission\",\n                    \"treatment_location_id\", \"walkin_sale_id\", \"is_a_split\" , \"split_details\",\n                    \"admission_request_id\", \"date_changed_by\", \"date_adjusted_from\", \"moved\", \"changes_track\",\n                    \"moved_from_chargesheet\", \"paid\", \"dispensed\", \"is_interim\", \"price\", \"dispensed_quantity\",\n                    \"administered_quantity\")->first()->toArray();\n\n                $record['is_interim'] = true;\n\n                $record['paid'] = true;\n\n                $newP  = Prescriptions::create($record);\n\n                $data = $p->payment->toArray();\n\n                unset($data['prescription_id']);\n\n                $pricing = $newP->payment()->create([$data]);\n\n                $pricing->update([\n                    'split_bill_id' => $split_bill->id,\n                    'invoiced' => $invoice->id,\n                    'price' => $data['price'],\n                    'discount' => $data['discount'],\n                    'amount' => $data['amount'],\n                    'quantity' => $data['quantity'],\n                    'complete' => $data['complete']\n                ]);\n\n            }  else if($type == 'investigation')\n            {\n                $p = Investigations::find($item['item_id']);\n                $clone = clone $p;\n                $newInvestigation = Investigations::create($clone->toArray());\n                $newInvestigation->is_interim = true;\n                $newInvestigation->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                $newInvestigation->invoiced = $invoice->id;\n                $newInvestigation->save();\n\n            } else if($type == 'consumable')\n            {\n                $p = Consumable::find($item['item_id']);\n                $clone = clone $p;\n                $newCons = Consumable::create($clone->toArray());\n                $newCons->is_interim = true;\n                $newCons->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                $newCons->invoice_id = $invoice->id;\n                $newCons->save();\n            } else if($type == 'Ward charge')\n            {\n                $p = InpatientVisitWard::find($item['item_id']);\n                $clone = clone $p;\n                $newInp = InpatientVisitWard::create($clone->toArray());\n                $newInp->is_interim = true;\n                $newInp->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                $newInp->invoice_id = $invoice->id;\n                $newInp->save();\n            } else if($type == 'Admission + Daily charges')\n            {\n                $p = InpatientVisitCharge::find($item['item_id']);\n                $clone = clone $p;\n                $newInvCharge = InpatientVisitCharge::create($clone->toArray());\n                $newInvCharge->invoice_id = $invoice->id;\n                $newInvCharge->is_interim = true;\n                $newInvCharge->split_bill_id = $split_bill->id;\n                $newInvCharge->save();\n            } else if($type == 'rebate') {\n                if(!$this->rebate_updated) {\n                    $visit_rebate = InpatientVisitRebate::findOrFail($item['item_id']);\n\n                    $company =  Insurance::where('name', 'NHIF')->first();\n\n                    $scheme = $company->schemes()->where('name', 'LIKE', '%' . 'universal' . '%')->first();\n\n                    if(!$visit_rebate->invoice_id)  {\n                        $inv = new Invoice;\n                        $inv->invoice_no = finance_generate_invoice_no();\n                        $inv->invoice_no_prefix = m_setting('finance.invoice_prefix') ? m_setting('finance.invoice_prefix') : 'INV';\n                        $inv->visit = $split_bill->visit_id;\n                        $inv->user_id = doe()->id;\n                        $inv->amount = $item['price'];\n                        $inv->company_id = $company->id;\n                        $inv->scheme_id = @$scheme->id;\n                        $inv->save();\n\n                        $visit_rebate->update([\n                            'invoice_id' => $inv->id\n                        ]);\n\n                        $this->rebate_updated = true;\n\n                        $this->saveInvoiceItems($inv, $data);\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * save invoice items (keep state)\n     * @param $invoice\n     * @param $data\n     */\n    public function saveInvoiceItems($invoice, $data)\n    {\n        $keys = [\n            'investigation',\n            'prescription',\n            'consumable',\n            'Admission + Daily charges',\n            'copay',\n            'Ward charge',\n            'rebate',\n            'Theatre clinician fee',\n            'Theatre fee'\n        ];\n\n        $items = collect(array_reverse($data['selected']))->groupBy('type')->toArray();\n\n        foreach($keys as $key) {\n            if(array_key_exists($key, $items)) {\n                foreach($items[$key] as $bill) {\n                    $invoice->invoiceItems()->create([\n                        'item_id' => $bill['item_id'],\n                        'item_type' => $bill['type'],\n                        'item_name' => $bill['name'],\n                        'price' => $bill['price'],\n                        'units' => $bill['quantity'],\n                        'amount' => $bill['amount'],\n                    ]);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n
